&lt;img alt=&quot;Dad&quot; title=&quot;Dad&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;dad.1debf0755d6d2fe2.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;dad.745efe67e560979e.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;dad.1debf0755d6d2fe2.webp 1024w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;dad.ae49a8c063720008.webp 2048w&quot; class=&quot;framed&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;🍻 Portrait of my dad for his birthday (today), I had this printed on his birthday card (Sketch a day prompt: &quot;print&quot;). 🎉🎂&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I spent longer on this than the usual daily sketches. It took a little over a week, doing an hour or two each day.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Source: A photo I took of him at a pub in Whitby.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</description>
